{"tid":619802,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"開始累了","createTime":"2018-04-07T04:25:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-07T10:24:57.000Z","uid":90102,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1f23755dd7acf1d798120d05f4049a6a0a86a2a2","tid":619802,"uid":90102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T04:25:04.000Z","msg":"我知女仔係要人氹 食軟唔食硬<br />\n<br />\n所以本身都盡量咩事都就哂佢 佢大哂<br />\n<br />\n次次同佢一講多少少就話我比說話佢聽<br />\n<br />\n相反當我做啲野唔合佢心意就係咁屌鳩我<br />\n<br />\n自己都想去引佢笑返 但又話依樣唔啱嗰樣唔啱<br />\n<br />\n到我唔開心都要照氹佢 佢就話 乜你都會識氹人嫁咩？<br />\n<br />\n我個下已經嬲都唔想嬲 只係覺得好失落<br />\n<br />\n咩都為佢著想 到依加開始發覺 自己唔係咁想再付出<br />\n<br />\n真係好攰<br />\n<br />\n純粹發洩下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccc93d4df51e03f589b1a76672cec5aab9e063a4","tid":619802,"uid":68081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T04:28:30.000Z","msg":"冇辦法，你冇樣冇身材，代遇唔好是常識吧<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n下個更恐怖，一於頂硬上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"335491008600e15fd8b085f20b3e4f0235ae4854","tid":619802,"uid":165024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T04:32:14.000Z","msg":"最後都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b085f7475f1844c4c1517f1cb98e20d819f7e097","tid":619802,"uid":90102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ccc93d4df51e03f589b1a76672cec5aab9e063a4","tid":619802,"uid":68081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T04:28:30.000Z","msg":"冇辦法，你冇樣冇身材，代遇唔好是常識吧<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n下個更恐怖，一於頂硬上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T04:37:30.000Z","msg":"係自己本身性格會成全人地 而唔計較自己hurt姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n樣同身材呢啲，叫做吸引到女朋友就夠啦"},{"pid":"d16004a2f3c6d3b51a1f9a3d074c36